description:
This trivia game is a template that could be reused for games or as a quiz when learning new things (i.e history, languages, etc. ). 

It uses a multiple-answer format to quiz users of various questions.
name: SineadTriviaGame
shortDescription: Sinead's Trivia Game is built as a template for trivia games for developers to use and for team members an opportunity to get to know each other.
